WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.605
Hey, good morning everybody. I just wanted to come on here and tell you some more things the Lord has showed me in prayer time.

00:00:08.606 --> 00:00:15.664
I'll tell you some positive things, some good things, but I have to tell you this first, and this is not so good.

00:00:15.665 --> 00:00:25.414
I want to be uplifting. I don't want to stir up fear or make anybody afraid, but I have to tell you what the Holy Spirit is telling me.

00:00:25.415 --> 00:00:32.727
There are things that we can avoid and some things I don't think we can.

00:00:32.728 --> 00:00:39.750
I feel I'm a watchman, like I've said, and it's my job to tell you what's going on.

00:00:39.751 --> 00:00:45.998
There was a massive barge traveling down the Mississippi River.

00:00:45.999 --> 00:00:51.190
I could see rust on the side of this barge; it was like a big boat.

00:00:51.191 --> 00:00:59.919
It was supposedly carrying grain or something out of the north somewhere. There was black all around the top of it.

00:00:59.920 --> 00:01:04.609
The area where the captain or the person who drives the boat sits was white and had rust on it.

00:01:04.610 --> 00:01:15.182
It looked like it was weathered. There was a little square opening on the deck part.

00:01:15.183 --> 00:01:24.776
They were moving, went out into the Gulf of Mexico, and turned their boat to face east.

00:01:24.777 --> 00:01:33.134
They opened the hatch and put out a rocket. They lifted it up.

00:01:33.135 --> 00:01:48.486
The men on this boat were Asian; I have no idea if it was China or whatever, but they raised this rocket up.

00:01:48.487 --> 00:02:00.873
It was about five feet tall and probably about a foot to two feet thick at the most.

00:02:00.874 --> 00:02:15.870
It was black and white and had USSR written on the rocket. They shot the rocket out over America, and when they did, it exploded.

00:02:15.871 --> 00:02:25.206
But I kept hearing in the spirit realm, 'It's not going to get high enough.'That's what I was hearing.

00:02:25.207 --> 00:02:42.493
It went out over the Tennessee and Kentucky area, Atlanta, Mississippi, Alabama, and then it went up by Ohio and exploded right over all that area.

00:02:42.494 --> 00:02:48.270
When it did, it was an EMP, and the EMP turned out all the lights.

00:02:48.271 --> 00:03:05.163
Because it didn't get high enough, it didn't have a blast radius that affected everything way over to the west, but it affected all of Virginia and Pennsylvania.

00:03:05.164 --> 00:03:15.173
It was terrible; complete darkness was over this area. The further west you went, it wasn't as dark, and things weren't affected as badly.

00:03:15.174 --> 00:03:34.592
I could see that people in places like Colorado did not have cell phones, internet, or cable TV.

00:03:34.593 --> 00:03:42.335
They had TVs with bunny ears and landline telephones, and they still had electricity.

00:03:42.336 --> 00:03:51.383
You weren't able to have a whole bunch of stuff going; the power grid was really weak, but you were still able to power things.

00:03:51.384 --> 00:04:00.350
I don't understand it all; I just see things whenever I'm praying. I could see the emergency broadcast come on.

00:04:00.351 --> 00:04:04.276
I could hear it, and they were warning the people of what happened.

00:04:04.277 --> 00:04:13.565
You know how they warn you with the emergency broadcast alerts on our TVs?

00:04:13.566 --> 00:04:22.227
They ran that because it turned the TV on, and you could hear the emergency broadcast going off.

00:04:22.228 --> 00:04:38.638
I had some friends call the landline at my house, and they asked, 'Do you have power?'I said, 'Yes.'I went to my refrigerator, opened it up, and there was still a light on inside.

00:04:38.639 --> 00:04:54.304
Looking out south, I could see in the spirit realm that the sycamore trees had leaves on them. It was still really warm outside.

00:04:54.305 --> 00:05:11.064
Whenever I'm seeing in the spirit and the Lord is showing me something, I always try to pay attention to my surroundings: the trees, the weather, and the warmth outside, how it feels, you know, how I would have assumed it to feel, where the sun is at, everything.

00:05:11.065 --> 00:05:14.762
I try to pay attention because you can always tell where we are in the season.

00:05:14.763 --> 00:05:32.844
The sun was setting more towards the southwest, so it was a summer month, probably late summer.

00:05:32.845 --> 00:05:39.152
So, this was basically the end of it, but it was a warning of an EMP attack upon our nation.

00:05:39.153 --> 00:05:48.119
I know it's a heavy message, but I want to tell you about things that the Lord shows me to pray about.

00:05:48.120 --> 00:05:54.400
It's not to stir up fear; I believe we can stop things through intercessory prayer.

00:05:54.401 --> 00:06:02.484
I tell people this stuff to warn you to pray. Thank you so much for watching this video.

00:06:02.485 --> 00:06:10.180
Hopefully, it didn't freak you out too bad. Have a blessed day, everybody.

